This paper deals with the design of UAV trajectories for data collection, which involves wireless communication between the UAV and ground terminals. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also considers the energy consumption of the UAV, which suggests that it may belong to cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the optimization of the UAV trajectory and GT transmit power involves mathematical modeling and optimization, which could place the paper in cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
